the costs, timing and outcome of post-approval clinical studies which FDA has required us to perform as part of the approval for Qsymia and STENDRA;
·
the cost required to maintain the REMS program for Qsymia;
·
results within the clinical trial programs for Qsymia and STENDRA or other results or decisions affecting the development of our investigational drug candidates;
·
announcements of technological innovations or new products by us or our competitors;
